headline: Analysts Diverge on Synopsys (SNPS) as Valuation Concerns Meet Strong AI-Driven Tailwinds
summary: Synopsys, Inc. (NASDAQ:SNPS) is one of the AI stocks analysts are betting on. Wells Fargo revised its outlook on Synopsys on November 25, trimming the price target to $445 from $550 while maintaining an Equal Weight rating.
